<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>Consultation Request Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f3f9fe;
            color: #34495e;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        @keyframes slideIn {
            0% {
                transform: translateY(-20px);
                opacity: 0;
            }
            100% {
                transform: translateY(0);
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }
        .email-container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            animation: slideIn 0.6s ease-out;
        }
        .email-header {
            background-color: #4caf50;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px;
            border-top-left-radius: 10px;
            border-top-right-radius: 10px;
        }
        .email-header h2 {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 26px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .email-header p {
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .email-body {
            padding: 20px 30px;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #4a4a4a;
        }
        .email-body p {
            margin-bottom: 18px;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }
        .email-body strong {
            color: #2c3e50;
        }
        .email-body a {
            color: #4caf50;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .email-body a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .email-footer {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #718096;
            border-bottom-left-radius: 10px;
            border-bottom-right-radius: 10px;
        }
        .email-footer a {
            color: #4caf50;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .email-footer a:hover {
            color: #2e7d32;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="email-header">
            <h2>Consultation Request Confirmed!</h2>
            <p>We’re excited to connect with you!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <p>Dear <strong><%= firstName %></strong>,</p>
            <p>Thank you for reaching out to us. We have successfully received your request for a consultation and are thrilled to assist you.</p>
            <p>Our team is currently reviewing your request and will get in touch with you shortly to finalize the details. Here’s what you can expect next:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>A confirmation of your preferred time slot or alternate suggestions.</li>
                <li>Details of your consultation meeting.</li>
                <li>Answers to any preliminary questions you might have shared.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>If you need to update your preferences or have any additional queries, please don’t hesitate to <a href="mailto:support@palikagis.com">contact our support team</a>.</p>
            <p>We’re here to ensure your consultation experience is seamless and valuable. Let’s make great things happen together!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>Best regards,</p>
            <p><strong>Palika GIS Team</strong></p>
            <p><a href="mailto:support@palikagis.com">support@palikagis.com</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
